{"tid":1972460,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"喺再有行動之前有兩樣嘢應該要改","createTime":"2020-04-14T13:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T15:28:51.000Z","uid":311544,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"75a6ce6442252383d83d03d2b7179b47c18cb3f5","tid":1972460,"uid":311544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T13:47:45.000Z","msg":"根據過往嗰幾個月嘅經驗，我覺得有嘢可以再改進下， 雖然文長， 但係都希望大家可以畀啲時間睇下<br />\n<br />\n以往幾個月每逢有啲咩事嘅時候，都係求其攞遮用， 就算遮陣都係全部係一啲唔透光嘅遮<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eiAo5rZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeiAo5rZ.png&h=55b85974&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實下一次開始大家可唔可以試下用啲<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">透明透光嘅遮</span></span></strong>？<br />\n起碼都開嘅時候唔會擋住你視線， 令到啲你可以睇到對面嘅一舉一動， 咁嘅話就算有咩事上嚟都可以靈活好多。原理就好似啲防暴嘅盾咁樣， 畀你睇到嘢之餘又有一定嘅防護。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yfqgF1z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyfqgF1z.jpg&h=eeef9d50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其次， 就算係和理非都好，出去嘅時候麻煩帶多樣嘢，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">嘗試帶多一支噴霧， 咩噴霧都得， 最好就好似定型水（ 即係攞嚟gel完頭噴一下嗰啲呢）</span></span></strong>， 呢一種黏性而且噴落對眼痛到仆街嘅噴霧， 作用係咩唔使多講喇。 依家尤其是身邊周圍都可能有便衣狗， 有咩事上嚟直接噴眼肯定最方便。 就算有手足比便衣狗咬， 喺防暴嚟到之前對住佢對狗眼噴一嘢， 都足夠令到隻狗失平衡，然後令到手足可以獲救。 而且呢啲定型水咁嘅噴霧帶出街一定唔犯法， 我鍾意喺街gel頭你吹呀， 所以和理非都可以安心咁帶， 而且又唔大支喎， 20蚊就有交易。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MJ3NNKR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMJ3NNKR.jpg&h=08114c90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有其他建議歡迎一齊討論，sorry for 1999"},{"pid":"fa80410288843408bb39d25d42472208ef81e218","tid":1972460,"uid":311544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T13:49:30.000Z","msg":"小弟用少少時間打出嚟的，希望大家可以畀啲心機睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23580cb337518cc8967bed21582c21ce688e64a2","tid":1972460,"uid":311544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T13:49:44.000Z","msg":"有錯歡迎批評"},{"pid":"d50996cf986e43b01548c88af279c1be75b450ef","tid":1972460,"uid":311544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T13:49:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"05db73fd00fce47ca0ee2448bb531bdaf4e27ffa","tid":1972460,"uid":311544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T13:50:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"88ffc863c6865deb0bd91447c10f03b2249b86f9","tid":1972460,"uid":311544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T13:51:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"44c89f4ec59a05e34ce5345f4f1a22e60044a581","tid":1972460,"uid":311544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T13:51:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b9249c289a82b878ac51c1a28b9e5f958b88d769","tid":1972460,"uid":311544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T13:52:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ec0f460da42f641c92e9285e42a0b83fa8c7f227","tid":1972460,"uid":311544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T13:52:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"96c740bc4fcca9ca9df4326a038ea867b67d06d8","tid":1972460,"uid":311544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T13:52:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d4e3deceab801a041769c1f4e1a8f431cc8e2030","tid":1972460,"uid":311544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T13:52:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"33dfabb506799f8c9a939e673a6f054d53f98ad1","tid":1972460,"uid":311544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T13:53:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fa0a3be5bef8647aa29528ab7c163c2de9759862","tid":1972460,"uid":311544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T13:53:52.000Z","msg":"push arrrrrr"},{"pid":"9c3f03e3a7db3f5c4d7527471e6a393c164bed26","tid":1972460,"uid":311544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T13:54:23.000Z","msg":"pushhh"},{"pid":"b070e517032e4ffd72e4a3d7e412e790a68ab6bb","tid":1972460,"uid":31